    <briefdescription>
<para>Memory Banks Driver APIs. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This contains APIs for a system-wide memory management driver to track page usage within memory banks.</para>
<para><simplesect kind="note"><para>The caller of these functions needs to ensure proper locking to protect the data when using these APIs. </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
